name: ExtensionVirtualServiceDetail
title: Cross-version Extension `R5.VirtualServiceDetail` for use in FHIR R4
description: This cross-version extension represents the FHIR R5 element `VirtualServiceDetail` for use in FHIR R4.
purpose:
This extension is part of the cross-version definitions generated to enable use of the
element `VirtualServiceDetail` as defined in FHIR R5
in FHIR R4.

The source element is defined as:
`VirtualServiceDetail` 0..* `VirtualServiceDetail`

Across FHIR versions, the element set has been mapped as:
* R5 `VirtualServiceDetail` 0..* `VirtualServiceDetail`

Following are the generation technical comments:
Element `VirtualServiceDetail` is not mapped to FHIR R4, since FHIR R5 `VirtualServiceDetail` is not mapped.
